@startuml
[*] --> Running
Running --> ConfigMode : configuration or power-saving settings required
ConfigMode --> Running : configuration completed
Running --> DataCollection : clock trigger
DataCollection --> Running : activity complete
Running --> SummaryPreparation : prepare summary
SummaryPreparation --> Running : activity complete
Running --> StatusCheck : status check request
StatusCheck --> Running : activity complete
Running --> ControlledMode : remote control
ControlledMode --> Shutdown : shutdown command
Shutdown --> [*] : shutdown condition
@enduml
